{"timestamp":"2026-04-23T14:48:58.720Z","provider":"elevenlabs","endpoint":"tts/m0OQuJtWCw1V23P0pQmG","kind":"voiceover","input":{"text":"Раньше я вставал затемно. Чайник свистит, жена режет хлеб. Тихо — чтоб детей не разбудить.","model_id":"eleven_multilingual_v2","voice_id":"m0OQuJtWCw1V23P0pQmG"},"output":{"local":"/Users/maximovchinnikov/github/ugc-cli/workspace/projects/soviet-engineer-001/assets/voiceover/clip-01-morning-kitchen.mp3","bytes":109549},"status":"ok","latency_ms":2895,"note":"clip-01-morning-kitchen VO"}
{"timestamp":"2026-04-23T14:48:59.982Z","provider":"elevenlabs","endpoint":"tts/m0OQuJtWCw1V23P0pQmG","kind":"voiceover","input":{"text":"Иду в цех. Снег скрипит под сапогами, фонари жёлтые. Все идут в одну сторону.","model_id":"eleven_multilingual_v2","voice_id":"m0OQuJtWCw1V23P0pQmG"},"output":{"local":"/Users/maximovchinnikov/github/ugc-cli/workspace/projects/soviet-engineer-001/assets/voiceover/clip-02-walk-to-factory.mp3","bytes":99100},"status":"ok","latency_ms":1260,"note":"clip-02-walk-to-factory VO"}
{"timestamp":"2026-04-23T14:49:01.399Z","provider":"elevenlabs","endpoint":"tts/m0OQuJtWCw1V23P0pQmG","kind":"voiceover","input":{"text":"Свой станок знаешь как свою руку. Гудит. Масло, металл. Работаешь — и не замечаешь времени.","model_id":"eleven_multilingual_v2","voice_id":"m0OQuJtWCw1V23P0pQmG"},"output":{"local":"/Users/maximovchinnikov/github/ugc-cli/workspace/projects/soviet-engineer-001/assets/voiceover/clip-03-shop-floor.mp3","bytes":115400},"status":"ok","latency_ms":1417,"note":"clip-03-shop-floor VO"}
{"timestamp":"2026-04-23T14:49:03.662Z","provider":"elevenlabs","endpoint":"tts/m0OQuJtWCw1V23P0pQmG","kind":"voiceover","input":{"text":"Обед в столовой. Щи. Котлета с пюре. Компот из сухофруктов. Двадцать копеек.","model_id":"eleven_multilingual_v2","voice_id":"m0OQuJtWCw1V23P0pQmG"},"output":{"local":"/Users/maximovchinnikov/github/ugc-cli/workspace/projects/soviet-engineer-001/assets/voiceover/clip-04-canteen-tray.mp3","bytes":110385},"status":"ok","latency_ms":2262,"note":"clip-04-canteen-tray VO"}
{"timestamp":"2026-04-23T14:49:05.423Z","provider":"elevenlabs","endpoint":"tts/m0OQuJtWCw1V23P0pQmG","kind":"voiceover","input":{"text":"Вечером домой. Тот же снег, те же фонари. Только в окне уже свет — ждут.","model_id":"eleven_multilingual_v2","voice_id":"m0OQuJtWCw1V23P0pQmG"},"output":{"local":"/Users/maximovchinnikov/github/ugc-cli/workspace/projects/soviet-engineer-001/assets/voiceover/clip-05-walk-home-evening.mp3","bytes":87397},"status":"ok","latency_ms":1760,"note":"clip-05-walk-home-evening VO"}
{"timestamp":"2026-04-23T14:49:06.852Z","provider":"elevenlabs","endpoint":"tts/m0OQuJtWCw1V23P0pQmG","kind":"voiceover","input":{"text":"Жена, дети, горячий ужин. Телевизор тихо бормочет. Тогда не знали, что это было счастье. Просто жили.","model_id":"eleven_multilingual_v2","voice_id":"m0OQuJtWCw1V23P0pQmG"},"output":{"local":"/Users/maximovchinnikov/github/ugc-cli/workspace/projects/soviet-engineer-001/assets/voiceover/clip-06-family-dinner.mp3","bytes":120834},"status":"ok","latency_ms":1428,"note":"clip-06-family-dinner VO"}
